{"tid":321920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"DQ案：民主派集會500人出席　高叫釋法可恥","createTime":"2017-07-14T12:51:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T16:47:37.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"48cee90cc69c57a58d4771a9d328a39c67e6fe0a","tid":321920,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:51:43.000Z","msg":"「長毛」梁國雄、劉小麗、羅冠聰和姚松炎4人下午被高院裁定褫奪立法會議員資格，民主派晚上8時在俗稱公民廣場的政總前地外舉行反DQ集會，集會至晚上8時半約有500人出席，警方開放一段添美道予集會人士。大部分民主派議員均出現撐場，新同盟范國威 、進師盟韓連山等亦有現身，他們高叫「人大釋法可恥、濫用程序可恥」。 <br />\n<br />\n集會開始時，4名被取消資格的議員上台，獲支持者掌聲。梁國雄指釋法曲解法律，用4名不喜歡的議員開刀，對於政府和香港法院主動濫用司法程序，改寫9月4日香港人的選擇感可恥。他估計未來會有其他的議員，以同一方式被褫奪資格，但劉曉波和劉霞的事令他們勇氣百倍。 <br />\n<br />\n姚松炎指，今日是香港政治最黑暗的一日，未來會靠民主派議員繼續守護立法會。他又指，今日是民主運動重要的一步，呼籲市民用方法令民主派可以重奪立法會。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劉小麗稱，香港今日變天，因為失去6名民主派議員，民主派失去了在分組點票失去最終否決權。但她指，就算失望不能絕望，要繼續為這片土地上的人而戰，重奪民主戰場。 <br />\n<br />\n羅冠聰強調，不會在民主運動中退下來，指議員只是其中一個身份，他同時是抗爭者和組織者，政府不能透過壓迫令他在人格上妥協，指在民主運動中不會退縮。他又指，改善不止在制度之內，亦在制度之外，民主運動不會因此而完結，呼籲市民不要沮喪，收起落寞的心情。 <br />\n---<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170714/mobile/bkn-20170714200810123-0714_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170714%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170714200810123-0714_00822_001.html&d=AV8D4jVDMEaXT1H5LwPgJW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=87465b04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170714/mobile/bkn-20170714200810123-0714_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n￼"},{"pid":"2186452898eaa933fc8cbae8d8ddcba118bcb4cd","tid":321920,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:30:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8206b2bd0c79cce8caa02f9c3861033422c52f","tid":321920,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71c676c28ee12be39b4ea85290d87df4f084a089","tid":321920,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:32:28.000Z","msg":"邊個最可恥？"},{"pid":"9b9743851c11da999740e520240b494bda6fb010","tid":321920,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:39:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"185e852e46a1c9efe3bcdb58bf380e81d3b0c8f6","tid":321920,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:35:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a4396e19a2abbfc56893334f23c2cdc674ef443","tid":321920,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:35:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c76f28ef78605b6a9359f60d24760a1ab53cc829","tid":321920,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:39:54.000Z","msg":"得五百人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5023ee1327f8a57141cf3e696df8439b5482ef77","tid":321920,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:40:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e7d2b0f3d3652d563a3f710e8ee5e5e71d3a147","tid":321920,"uid":36300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:40:39.000Z","msg":"因報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f1278779f0a8c8676ef8c0e360eec82e1c4f84","tid":321920,"uid":76421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:58:14.000Z","msg":"100人我就信"},{"pid":"c433cedc4df3ff16d3ec0050d7be2faea0066d73","tid":321920,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:45:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日是香港政治最黑暗的一日</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全盛時期既香港可以有幾多個最黑暗日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61257cfa8a2f3a9df9ff2892a9df676df09b6cc6","tid":321920,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:47:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得五百人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今次我都估唔到得五百人&hellip;<br />\n諗住起碼係民族黨集會十倍"},{"pid":"9d1288d0bf7246902e4a705e163ccf39a2683589","tid":321920,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:47:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日是香港政治最黑暗的一日</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全盛時期既香港可以有幾多個最黑暗日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n365日"}]}